{"tid":202972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩靠嚇晒導彈　北韓：美動武即爆核戰","createTime":"2017-04-16T02:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T02:49:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"294711c4d50bbd8539e9acd5ca1f58a4493dc355","tid":202972,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"金正恩靠嚇晒導彈<br />\n北韓：美動武即爆核戰<br />\n<br />\n跟過去幾場大型閱兵不同，在平壤金日成廣場檢閱台上的北韓領導人金正恩，身旁並不見盟友中國派官員出席撐場，但也無損他的興致，罕有身穿西裝的金正恩，不時向台下的軍民揮手，或跟總理朴奉珠等官員交談。正當外界猜測北韓會否無視中美反對，執意昨天就進行第六次核試之際，獨家轉播朝鮮中央電視台畫面的南韓聯合通訊社旗下聯合新聞TV，卻在字幕上打出「今天似乎不會核試──可能於25日建軍節試爆。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20170416&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=19991549\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170416%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D19991549&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e3cdf7c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170416%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D19991549&h=217b6c0c\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20170416&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=19991549</a>"},{"pid":"446b747f5582d788c0af34a12732cd9759883d81","tid":202972,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"射個核彈，點知係北韓境內就爆左"},{"pid":"bc71ec69f45fb6fcb47ac0336b42bf549b9158d0","tid":202972,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/f45DV6D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ff45DV6D.gif&h=e7c42a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/f45DV6D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ff45DV6D.gif&h=e7c42a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/f45DV6D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ff45DV6D.gif&h=